    <abstract id="aspace_cabbf906888c58c6a4a0e9f02f46c724">Don Stitt is an actor, writer, director, choreographer and composer who began his career in the mid 1960s. He received his MFA from WCSU in 2007. The collection includes his written work created throughout his career in the theater.</abstract>
